“giri più convessi e più staccati” [more convex and detached whorls —with respect to 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB75FFC6FF74EDF4FDF7F843" authority="(Donovan, 1804)" authorityName="Donovan" authorityYear="1804" baseAuthorityName="Donovan" baseAuthorityYear="1804" box="[151,539,1989,2015]" class="Gastropoda" family="Pyramidellidae" genus="Turbonilla" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="11" pageNumber="354" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="acuta">
