</taxonomicName>
].
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C30D69A9EB72FFC1FF24EAA8FDF7FE17" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA83A22EB72FFC1FF24EAA8FDF7FE17" blockId="12.[151,1436,153,395]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB72FFC1FF24EAA8FED1FF2F" bold="true" box="[199,317,153,179]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355">Remarks:</emphasis>
having been instituted on the basis of insignificant morphological characteristics, we rank it infrasubspecific, and thus not available (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB72FFC1FDF1EA8CFD75FF4B" author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[530,665,189,215]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 
<date id="FFA91CE2EB72FFC1FD34EA8CFCDBFF4B" box="[727,823,188,215]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" value="1945-10-02">10.2, 45</date>
.5, 45.6, glossary). This saves 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB72FFC1FB6AEA8CFEC4FF67" authority="Thiele, 1930" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1930" class="Gastropoda" family="Pyramidellidae" genus="Turbonilla" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="scalariformis">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB72FFC1FB6AEA8CFA70FF4B" box="[1161,1436,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="355">Turbonilla scalariformis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB72FFC1FF74EAD0FEC4FF67" author="Thiele, J." box="[151,296,225,251]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" pagination="561 - 596" refId="ref19401" refString="Thiele, J. (1930) Gastropoda und Bivalvia. In: Michaelsen, W. &amp; Hartmeyer, R. (Eds.), Die Fauna Sudwest-Australiens. Ergebnisse der Hamburger Sudwest-Australischen Forschungsreise (1905). Vol. 5. Gustav Fischer, Jena, pp. 561 - 596, pl. 4." type="journal article" year="1930">Thiele, 1930</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, a taxon described from Oyster Harbour, Albany (
<collectingCountry id="F3007AB2EB72FFC1FCB9EAD0FC28FF60" box="[858,964,225,252]" name="Australia" pageId="12" pageNumber="355">Australia</collectingCountry>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB72FFC1FC39EAD0FB8BFF67" author="Thiele, J." box="[986,1127,225,251]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" pagination="561 - 596" refId="ref19401" refString="Thiele, J. (1930) Gastropoda und Bivalvia. In: Michaelsen, W. &amp; Hartmeyer, R. (Eds.), Die Fauna Sudwest-Australiens. Ergebnisse der Hamburger Sudwest-Australischen Forschungsreise (1905). Vol. 5. Gustav Fischer, Jena, pp. 561 - 596, pl. 4." type="journal article" year="1930">Thiele 1930</bibRefCitation>
). Reported again by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB72FFC1FAB3EAD0FF02FE83" author="Bellini, R." pageId="12" pageNumber="355" pagination="1 - 87" refId="ref15827" refString="Bellini, R. (1929 a) I molluschi del Golfo di Napoli (studi precedenti, l'ambiente, enumerazione e sinonimia). Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli, 6 (2), 1 - 87." type="journal article" year="1929">Bellini (1929a)</bibRefCitation>
as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB72FFC1FE43EB34FC86FE83" authority="Monterosato. Taking" authorityName="Monterosato. Taking" box="[416,874,261,287]" class="Gastropoda" family="Pyramidellidae" genus="Turbonilla" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="delicata">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB72FFC1FE43EB34FD95FE83" box="[416,633,261,287]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="355">Turbonilla delicata</emphasis>
Monterosato. Taking
</taxonomicName>
into account the complex taxonomy of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB72FFC1FF74EB18FE72FEDF" authority="Risso, 1826" authorityName="Risso" authorityYear="1826" box="[151,414,297,323]" class="Gastropoda" family="Pyramidellidae" genus="Turbonilla" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB72FFC1FF74EB18FEE1FEDF" box="[151,269,297,323]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="355">Turbonilla</emphasis>
Risso, 1826
</taxonomicName>
, as well as the poor description, the absence of figures attached to its original description, and the fact that it may fit several (not even congeneric) Mediterranean taxa, we are not able to understand what 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB72FFC1FF74EB40FEADFE17" author="Bellini, R." box="[151,321,369,395]" pageId="12" pageNumber="355" pagination="85 - 121" refId="ref15636" refString="Bellini, R. (1902 a) Contribuzione alla conoscenza della fauna dei molluschi marini dell'isola di Capri. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 1, 15, 85 - 121." type="journal article" year="1902">Bellini (1902a)</bibRefCitation>
actually described.
</paragraph>
